snippet.title: Amber Heard is taking a tropical vacation and posts photo showing off backside in swimsuit
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Posts Instagram Picture Showing Off Backside In White Swimsuit Amber Heard was seen on vacation wearing a white bathing suit, showing her assets for a portrait taken and posted on her official Instagram.

The Texas native is currently dating Heidi Klum's ex-boyfriend, Vito Schnabel, according to Us Weekly. He ended an intermittent relationship with Elon Musk in February 2018. Prior to his relationship with Musk, Heard was married to actor Johnny Depp from 2015-2017.

Variety reported that in May 2016, Tillet Wright, a mutual friend of the couple, called 911 at the actress' request.

Since separating from Depp, Heard has thrown herself into her film career and her charitable work. He is currently defending the cause of a 12-year-old Syrian refugee named Weam.

Amber explained to her millions of followers that the girl "needs a blood transfusion" and that her medical care was expensive. She has partnered with Crowdrise to help pay the girl's medical bills.
